Gallery for 20th Century Design. Open by appointment.
Shop our collection:

node.text: A pair of cast concrete tables by American artist, Scott Burton, currently greets visitors near the entrance of the main gallery.

node.text: Our new installation in the side gallery pairs a playful 1930s Swedish floor lamp with a restrained sofa by Kaare Klint in its original Nigerian leather.

node.text: Currently featured in the side gallery is a rare studio cabinet by Paul Evans. This model was produced circa 1962 with less than ten examples ever realized. Other pieces on display include a range of American, Italian, and Brazilian designs.
